features: 【Complete Package】Elevate your Stanley Cup experience with the LeadDock Stanley Cup Accessories Set, featuring 2pcs 0.4 Inch/10 MM Straw Cover Cap, 1Pcs Silicone Spill Proof Stopper for 6-10mm straw, 1pcs Name ID Letter Handle Charm, and 1Pcs Silicone Boot. Perfectly designed for Stanley 30&40 Oz Tumblers.

【Premium Quality Material】Crafted from high-quality silicone, this Accessories Set boasts durability, exquisite workmanship, clear patterns, and effective resistance against dust and splashes. An essential companion to the Stanley Travel Cup.

【Effective Protection】Our protective silicone boot is tailored for the Stanley Quencher Adventure 30&40 Oz Tumbler, providing excellent defense against scratches, slips, dents, and minimizing noise for a smoother experience.
【Practical and Adorable】Not just functional, this Stanley Cup Accessories Set adds a cute touch to your cup. It serves as a decoration while ensuring cleanliness and hygiene for your cups and straws.

【Perfect Gift Choice】Cute, practical, and suitable for decorating, this Stanley Cup Accessories Set makes for a perfect gift for yourself, friends, and family. Bring joy to their sipping moments with this thoughtful and versatile set.
